Category:  General  Topic:  give



Used to give an object, currently in inventory, to another person in the
same room (and visible to the giver of course).

syntax:  give <i_th> [object name]  <n_th> [critter name]

example:  give 2.orange baker
          give sword guard
          give 3 sword 1.guard

See also:  get, drop, wear, pay, donate, junk
